{"tid":1540991,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]食完TG腸胃唔妥你有咩計？","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:57:40.000Z","uid":235407,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c90945c6b96730ddc4e5e8210f6d1821f6f3dd55","tid":1540991,"uid":235407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"話說我諗好多手足試過發夢食完tg都會腸胃唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗多數人都係諗住隔一牌就無事，但係都有手足係一直keep住唔舒服&hellip;<br />\n小弟都叫理科出身，試過以下方法，希望大家俾啲意見：<br />\n<br />\nTG (CS gas)係有機化合物，而且好似話係晶體。<br />\n咁如果有手足一直腸胃唔好，我覺得係晶體一直殘留係體內。<br />\n咁好明顯飲水係沖佢唔走/溶唔到佢，好簡單有機物多數都唔溶於水。<br />\n所以，我諗方法溶左佢。有機而又落得肚嘅溶液，無錯，就係酒精！<br />\n我同另一個手足試過，飲烈酒個肚即刻舒服翻，最多係屙多一次。<br />\n<br />\n大家俾啲意見，因為雖然即時好有效，但唔知長遠會唔會有咩副作用&hellip;<br />\n暫時我唔係好見到網上有咩解決嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3728d9b4efed689a7a1bd4e52b0aac6a621ecf2c","tid":1540991,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29695708abaa86d16ec0bf0cc86d53eb3a006c30","tid":1540991,"uid":235407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"如果手足們有咩方法都攞出尼討論下"},{"pid":"9c03185bfeb966e9896522f23a1510e4ea380c7c","tid":1540991,"uid":317188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28d40027b534506c4e6ca1383efc9099a818232","tid":1540991,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c33fbcf497ab2d990022d1d77102cd587d7e7e8c","tid":1540991,"uid":235407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc